OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FA rather cloudy day with
OL,6,Ffurther spells of showery rain,
OL,7,Fpossibly heavy at times. A band of
OL,8,Fmore persistent rain and stronger
OL,9,Fwinds then arriving later in the
OL,10,Fafternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FRain
OL,13,Fclearing on Tuesday to a mix of
OL,14,Fsunshine and blustery showers. Further
OL,15,Fshowers possible on Wednesday, then
OL,16,Fturning drier, brighter and warmer on
OL,17,FThursday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
